Golden Arches in London 12 years ago.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999993399797, \"rank\": 6.600331533496033e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_McDonald\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5834318058997227e-45, \"text\": \"Ronald McDonald\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_McDonald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_McDonald\"}, {\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Arches\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Golden Arches\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Arches\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Arches\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 5.933461331550925e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"catering\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"Philipp Wurz\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"as much as 20 per cent\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"the meals\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's fair to reflect that it's a much healthier Olympics in Paris - no McDonald's, no chicken nuggets, more healthy food.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.327672198689269e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a much healthier Olympics\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"no McDonald\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"no chicken nuggets\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"more healthy food\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's definitely less junk food.\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"less junk food\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We really try to push the quality high,' Wurz said.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"Wurz\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We tried to come up with a very specific plan to promote the French know-how, the savoir faire of the French cuisine, which of course, has a reputation all over the planet.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9706253257930879, \"rank\": 0.023108712695814975, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French cuisine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very specific plan\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \", the savoir faire\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"a reputation\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'One very specific French feature that we have is our Michelin-starred chef kitchen, so twice per day the athletes can also go there and really discover very high-level French cuisine cooked on site by our Michelin-star chefs.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9706253257930879, \"rank\": 0.023108712695814975, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin-starred\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French cuisine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\"}, {\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin-star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have four of them and eight recipes, so this has become a very popular spot.'\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight recipes\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"a very popular spot\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games' fresh approach comes after McDonald's ended its Olympic sponsorship deal in the lead-up to the 2020 Games in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999799675666682, \"rank\": 1.9984969087410142e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games' fresh approach\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"McDonald\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympic sponsorship deal\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Games\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The food chain had been associated with the Games for 41 years and contributed as much as $1billion in every four-year cycle before the sponsorship deal was halted in 2017.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The food chain\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"41 years\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"every four-year cycle\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the sponsorship deal\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But while athletes are forced to do without Big Macs in the village, burgers and hot dogs will be among the athletes' options - just a little healthier and locally produced.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"Big Macs\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"burgers\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"hot dogs\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' options\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even the chefs' menus have been developed with sports nutritionists, so it's very high-level cuisine, still respecting what the athletes actually need,' Wurz continued.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even the chefs' menus\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"sports nutritionists\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"very high-level cuisine\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"Wurz\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Once the competition is over, they can also just let it go and fully profit on what everything France offers best.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999977918202427, \"rank\": 1.704953092990686e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"what everything\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We will also provide hot dogs and burgers, but not at the main dining hall - we have dedicated grab-and-go outlets where we still provide this.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hot dogs\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"burgers\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"the main dining hall\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"grab-and-go outlets\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, the meat is 100 per cent French origin and will be grilled in our kitchens.'\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2523, \"end\": 2529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9706253257930879, \"rank\": 0.023108712695814975, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the meat\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"our kitchens\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also an active commitment for vegetarian options to be more readily available at the Games, with plant-based nuggets the only variety of nugget on the table for athletes this summer - much to a certain Jamaican sprinter's horror, no doubt.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9991576426502272, \"rank\": 0.0008430669274520821, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an active commitment\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"vegetarian options\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"plant-based nuggets\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"the only variety\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"nugget\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The vegetalisation, the plant-based food, is one of the most important commitments,' Gregoire Bechu, the Games' sustainable food project manager, said.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2912, \"end\": 2920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Gregoire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7388038006936043e-20, \"text\": \"Gregoire\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Gregoire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Gregoire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vegetalisation\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"the plant-based food\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important commitments\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' sustainable food project manager\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toThe Times, chicken skewers, salmon fillets and margherita pizza have been the most requested meals for the Games' caterers, who are expected to provide upwards of 13 million meals across the Olympics and Paralympics.\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toThe Times\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"chicken skewers\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"salmon fillets\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"margherita pizza\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"the most requested meals\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' caterers\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"upwards of 13 million meals\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The very finest croissants and pains au chocolate, two of France's culinary staples, will be filling up hungry athletes at breakfast, while 12 separate cheeses are set to do the rounds over the coming weeks.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3268, \"end\": 3274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999977918202427, \"rank\": 1.704953092990686e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The very finest croissants\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"pains\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"chocolate\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"hungry athletes\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"breakfast\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"12 separate cheeses\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3369}, {\"ngram\": \"the rounds\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming weeks\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The cheeses are high level and well-known French cheeses such as Comte and Brie de Meaux,' Wurz added.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3462, \"end\": 3468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9706253257930879, \"rank\": 0.023108712695814975, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3485, \"end\": 3490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Count\", \"score\": 0.9876867263588894, \"rank\": 0.012419606358453837, \"text\": \"Comte\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Count\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Count\"}, {\"begin\": 3495, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brie_de_Meaux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brie de Meaux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brie_de_Meaux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brie_de_Meaux\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cheeses\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3431}, {\"ngram\": \"high level\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"Wurz\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Then we have very specific goat cheeses.\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very specific goat cheeses\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we have a total of 12 different cheeses that we have in rotation.'\", \"fro